    "For T 2, we chose only from HIGH sensitivity training queries whereas for T 1 and T 3, we chose 4 HIGH and 4 LOW sensitivity training queries.",
    "To identify the most similar queries from the training set, we used cosine similarity between their text embeddings which were obtained using a sentence transformer model foot_4.",
    "Tables 7 and 8 (in Appendix) show the prompts used for the tasks T 1, T 2, and T 3.",
    "We chose one open-source (Mistral-7B-Instruct) and one closed-source model (GPT-4o-mini) for our experiments.",
    "Please note that although the GPT-4o model is an external LLM, it is included just for comparison with other models."
